---
title: Mega Turkey Meatballs over Penne with Broccoli
description: Forget the itty, the bitty, and the miniature: there are some bigger, better, and bolder bad boys in town. These jumbo-sized turkey meatballs are guaranteed to shake things up at pasta night. Your family will ooh and ahh over their colossal size as well as the ooey-gooey cheese that drips from their tops—and equally astonished by how you managed to put together a tomato-y pasta and bites of broccoli at the same time (it’s easy when you cook both in the same pot).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mega-turkey-meatballs-7628d19c.jpg
